    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Booking
    Represents a booking in the movie booking system.
    BookingController
    REST controller for handling movie booking related requests.
    BookingDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a booking.
    BookingRepository
    Repository interface for managing Booking entities in the database.
    BookingRequestDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a booking request.
    BookingService
    Service class for managing booking-related operations.
    CustomUserDetailsService
    Service class implementing UserDetailsService for providing user details to Spring Security for authentication and authorization.
    Movie
    Represents a movie in the movie booking system.
    MovieBookingApplication
     
    MovieController
    REST controller for managing movie related requests.
    MovieDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a movie.
    MovieRepository
    Repository interface for managing Movie entities in the database.
    MovieService
    Service class for managing movie-related operations.
    OpenApiConfig
    Configuration class for setting up OpenAPI (Swagger) documentation.
    Seat
    Represents a seat in the movie booking system.
    SeatDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a seat.
    SeatRepository
    Repository interface for managing Seat entities in the database.
    SecurityConfig
    Configuration class for Spring Security settings.
    Showtime
    Represents a showtime for a movie in the movie booking system.
    ShowtimeController
    REST controller for managing showtime related requests.
    ShowtimeDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a showtime.
    ShowtimeRepository
    Repository interface for managing Showtime entities in the database.
    ShowtimeService
    Service class for managing showtime-related operations.
    User
    Represents a user in the movie booking system.
    UserController
    REST controller for managing user related requests, including registration, authentication, and user data retrieval.
    UserDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user.
    UserRepository
    Repository interface for managing User entities in the database.
    UserService
    Service class for managing user-related operations.
